node.text: When we went into lockdown last year we jumped to get a show out for you all that would be really helpful and it was fast and furious jools was my camra lady !! Since then I’ve been working On the recipes for my next book and series and they’re all done and tested, We start filming the meals for TV in July and on Sunday we put finishing touches on the soundtrack at the amazing @abbeyroadstudios who were a delight to work with and the talented @tobietripp who headed up the most amazing incredible string Quartet. In this next series I really want to do everything I can to inspire you to cook up the most wonderful memorable meals for the ones you love - this is about reconnecting over great food and I hope it will be a total feast for all the senses #JamiesTogether

node.text:
The National Food Strategy from Henry Dimbleby and his team is out today !! The Government now has 6 months to respond to this report to improve our kids’ health. So they might want to add this to their holiday reading!

Tag @borisjohnsonuk and @sajidjavidmp in the comments so we can make sure ALL children have access to decent, nutritious food, no matter where they live!

This is an incredible opportunity to make the food system fairer with ideas like bringing food education back into schools and asking businesses to step up to offer healthier options. Link in my bio for more info!

#NationalFoodStrategy
